// Smoke-test project-local deferred lighting BXDF, selected by smoke materials to satisfy the per-material BXDF
// requirement. Pulled into the cook-generated deferred lighting
// dispatch module (which #defines NWB_DEFERRED_BXDF_FUNCTION to this model's entry name). The deferred lighting
// framework (NwbBxdfSurface, the scene light list, the shadow accessor, the engine BRDF helpers) is in scope.
half3 NWB_DEFERRED_BXDF_FUNCTION(NwbBxdfSurface surface, int2 pixel){
    return nwbSceneApplyLighting(
        surface.baseColor,
        surface.normal,
        float4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0),
        surface.worldPosition,
        pixel,
        surface.indirectIrradiance
    );
}


